@wp.kernel
def expr_khvlno(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.8 - v0 + 0.14)) / (wp.cos(tmp + 0.45) * (v0 + 0.78 - v2 + 0.25)))
    v2 = v1
    tmp = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.13) - v2) + (wp.cos(v2 + 0.58) * 0.01))
    v0 = (v1 / (tmp * wp.sin(tmp + 0.15)))
    data[tid] = v0
